name: skyle_api
desc: Skyle API package.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: CalibrationRepository
desc: Interface for calibrating Skyle.

name: abort
desc: Aborts a calibration started by calibrate.

name: calcX
desc:
Calculates the calibration point x-axis coordinate value from the CalibrationPoints.array id and the width
of the screen in pixels.

name: calcY
desc:
Calculates the calibration point y-axis coordinate value from the CalibrationPoints.array id and the width
of the screen in pixels.

name: calibrate
desc: Starts a calibration which can be aborted with abort or finish by its own.

name: next
desc:
Triggers the next calibration point in case calibrate was called with the stepped option
being set to true.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: connect
desc: Starts the connection process of Skyle.

name: disconnect
desc: Disconnects Skyle and shuts down the reconnection cycle.

name: dispose
desc: Disposes the instance of ET completely.

name: softDisconnect
desc: Disconnects only the grpc client and makes it unusable.

name: testConnectClients
desc: Simulates a connection. This is only used for tests with the TestServer which is located in lib/src/test/test_server.dart

name: trySoftReconnect
desc:
TODO(krjw-eyev):  Add async cancellation if called again.
Trys to reconnect the grpc connection. Is only needed after calling softDisconnect
